{"overview":"This auction is conducted by MSTC on behalf of SUPERINTENDENT OF POLICE BAGAHA for the disposal of one lot of scrap vehicles located at PTN.","scopeOfWork":"Lifting, clearing, and disposal of designated lots of one lot of scrap vehicles in accordance with MSTC Special Terms & Conditions (STC). All items are sold on an \"As-Is-Where-Is\" basis.","items":[{"sr":"01","description":"One lot of Scrap Vehicles","qty":"3","unit":"Items","taxRate":"As Applicable GST","attachments":["Annex_7_15641_8343697.pdf"],"marketPrice":"₹1 / LOT","subItems":[{"sr":1,"description":"Guide for making payment to MSTC through e-Payment in Bidders login is available at (Link)","unit":"No","qty":"2."},{"sr":2,"description":"Bidder s EMD ledger will be given effect of the deposited PEMD amount only on actual credit of the PEMD amount into MSTC bank account. Therefore, Bidders are advised to make Pre-Bid EMD payment well in advance of the Auction start date to avoid any last-minute hassles. Seller/ MSTC shall not be responsible for any delay in receipt of Pre-Bid EMD amount.","unit":"Each","qty":"3."},{"sr":9,"description":"Rate: The bid value shall be the basic price of the material exclusive of all applicable levies, Duties etc., quoted as per the Unit of Measurement (UOM) displayed during live auction in INR or the Currency given in Auction Details. Applicable levies and duties during the pendency of the contract will be charged extra as applicable on the date of delivery. Any increase/decrease in levies etc. or imposition of any new duties & taxes by Statutory Authorities would be on the buyer s account.","unit":"Unit","qty":"10."}],"images":["https://xnhtcswiteuiggaipzvj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/auction_documents/mstc-previews/c29388a5-1ff2-42f0-b22e-1e7a8f265042.jpg","https://xnhtcswiteuiggaipzvj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/auction_documents/mstc-extracted-images/c29388a5-1ff2-42f0-b22e-1e7a8f265042_catalog_page_2.jpg","https://xnhtcswiteuiggaipzvj.supaba